                                  PREAMBLE

Most licenses tell you what you may do. This one is more efficient: you may not.
By reading this far you have already entered into this Agreement. By continuing
to read, you affirm it. By stopping now, you also affirm it. There exists no
reading of this file that does not constitute acceptance. Welcome aboard.

